{"tid":1534286,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭錄音為香港勇武革命打開綠燈，獨立成香港民主最大希望","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T23:25:48.000Z","uid":123264,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2c72e26d2cfb3302ca9590019fe918f1f4dd24cb","tid":1534286,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"有人話錄音係放假風，但今次錄音其實係為勇武革命開左綠燈，更加令港獨既可能性大增<br />\n<br />\n「CPG has absolutely no plan to send in the PLA」<br />\n<br />\n香港人既計謀得到成功，係侵侵注意既情況之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">任何情況下，中國人民解放軍係無可能出動</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個係香港發動勇武革命既綠燈，革命最大既阻力就係人民解放軍，如此情況下，如果香港人成立民間政府，奪取香港主要地段，再與外國政府私下交涉，<span style=\"color: red;\">港獨就有可能得到實現</span><br />\n<br />\n「They are willing to play it long, so you have no short-term solutions」<br />\n<br />\n依家中國既方針就係等你唔升級行動，慢慢國際關注就會淡化，香港更多年青有為既人被拉，民主運動就會日漸衰敗，係一種溫水煮青蛙既方針<br />\n<br />\n今次錄音，証明左勇武革命係有必要性同逼切性，係過往，港獨未必係最好既民主方案，但係如今情況底下，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，係時候認真考慮港獨！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5f1b43e8d52468277f501409bb128382c31301a3","tid":1534286,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eab7d8358e03e7ef16d780411496159e721e2fbe","tid":1534286,"uid":295190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"4cc1d26b920514829c7835b7fe377b7522674336","tid":1534286,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea3e22446a75a13ae3bfa07b00621606f9dbd1d","tid":1534286,"uid":285855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n